      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size must be sufficient to estimate hemolysis mean and standard deviation at each operating point; minimum n=6 replicates per condition required for MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Sample size characterisation was not performed. Available experimental data comprised n=3 replicates at most operating points, below the MRL 5 minimum. Statistical power of the validation comparison is unknown."
    },
