      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between simulation input parameters and experimental conditions must be formally assessed; any non-equivalencies must be quantified as validation uncertainty contributions.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment was not conducted. Differences in inlet velocity profile (flat profile in simulation vs. developed profile in experiment) were noted but not quantified as uncertainty contributions."
